Package com.spleefleague.core.player

Class CorePlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.spleefleague.core.database.variable.DBEntity
      • com.spleefleague.core.database.variable.DBPlayer
        • com.spleefleague.core.player.CoreOfflinePlayer
  • public class CorePlayer
extends DBPlayer
    CorePlayer is an instance of DBPlayer that maintains various options and stats unrelated to game modes, such as afk, ranking, and environment keys
